devdoc.details: A multi-signature wallet contract that requires multiple confirmations before executing transactions.

cancelTransaction(uint256).details: Allows an owner to cancel a transaction before it is executed.

confirmTransaction(uint256).details: Allows an owner to confirm a transaction.

constructor.details: Initializes the contract with a list of owners and the number of required confirmations.

getRequired().details: Returns the number of required confirmations.

getTransaction(uint256).details: Returns details of a specific transaction.

returns.canceled: Whether the transaction has been canceled
returns.executed: Whether the transaction has been executed

isConfirmed(uint256,address).details: Returns whether an owner has confirmed a transaction.

revokeConfirmation(uint256).details: Allows an owner to revoke a confirmation for a transaction.

submitTransaction(address,uint256,bytes).details: Allows an owner to submit a transaction.

returns.txIndex: The index of the submitted transaction
